
	plobdadmin - PLOB administration utility
	========================================

Heiko Kirschke
November 30, 1998

 - For plobdadmin to run, the library librpclientplob.so must be found
   in LD_LIBRARY_PATH (for UNIX) or in PATH (for Windows/NT).

 - The plobdadmin administration utility has help texts; call:
	~/plob-2.08>plobdadmin
	tcp://localhost/database>help
   to read the help text.

 - The directory scripts contains some example scripts which can be
   run by plobdadmin; see the comments in the example scripts for
   details.
